    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0036">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">• The borrowing entity has few or no other material assets or activities, and therefore little or no
independent capacity to repay the obligation, apart from the income that it receives from the
asset(s) being financed.</data>
      <data key="d4">Preamble</data>
    </node>
    <node id="SUBJ:The borrowing entity">
      <data key="d2">subject</data>
      <data key="d6">The borrowing entity</data>
    </node>
    <node id="COND:OBL-0036">
      <data key="d2">condition</data>
      <data key="d6">few or no other material assets or activities, and therefore little or no independent capacity to repay the obligation, apart from the income that it receives from the asset(s) being financed</data>
    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0037">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">The primary source of repayment of the obligation is the income
generated by the asset(s), rather than the independent capacity of the borrowing entity;</data>
      <data key="d4">Preamble</data>
      <data key="d5">repayment of the obligation must come from the income generated by the asset(s)</data>
    </node>
    <node id="COND:OBL-0037">
