    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0038">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">and
• The terms of the obligation give the lender a substantial degree of control over the asset(s) and
the income that it generates.</data>
      <data key="d4">Preamble</data>
      <data key="d5">have a substantial degree of control over the asset(s) and the income that it generates</data>
    </node>
