    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0176">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">Moreover, the following conditions will have to be met:
o For corporate entities (or the entity’s parent company), they must have securities
outstanding on a recognised securities exchange;</data>
