    <node id="OBL-0201">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">In particular, to be eligible for the
proposed ‘top-down’ treatment, purchased corporate receivables must satisfy the following conditions:
• The receivables are purchased from unrelated, third party sellers, and as such the bank has not
originated the receivables either directly or indirectly.</data>
      <data key="d4">Preamble</data>
      <data key="d5">purchase receivables only from unrelated, third party sellers</data>
    </node>
    <node id="COND:OBL-0201">
      <data key="d2">condition</data>
      <data key="d6">to be eligible for the proposed 'top-down' treatment</data>
    </node>
