    <node id="OBL-0202">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">58 Basel III: Finalising post-crisis reforms
• The receivables must be generated on an arm’s-length basis between the seller and the obligor.</data>
      <data key="d4">Preamble</data>
      <data key="d5">must be generated on an arm’s-length basis between the seller and the obligor</data>
    </node>
