    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0216">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">A voluntary return to the standardised or foundation approach is permitted
only in extraordinary circumstances, such as divestiture of a large fraction of the bank’s credit-related
business in that asset class, and must be approved by the supervisor.</data>
