    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0255">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">The maturity of such transactions must be calculated as the greater of one-day, and the effective
maturity (M, consistent with the definition above), except for transactions subject to a master netting
agreement, where the floor is determined by the minimum holding period for the transaction type, as
required by paragraph 113.</data>
      <data key="d4">Section XI</data>
