    <node id="OBL-0715">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">Unless specified differently below, banks must not take account of physical or financial collateral,
guarantees or other credit risk mitigation techniques to reduce the leverage ratio exposure measure, nor
may banks net assets and liabilities.</data>
      <data key="d4">Section XI</data>
      <data key="d5">must not take account of physical or financial collateral, guarantees or other credit risk mitigation techniques to reduce the leverage ratio exposure measure, nor may net assets and liabilities</data>
    </node>
