      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">Banks must include all balance sheet assets in their leverage ratio exposure measure, including
on-balance sheet derivatives collateral and collateral for SFTs, with the exception of on-balance sheet
derivative and SFT assets that are covered in paragraphs 32 to 56 below.11
29.</data>
      <data key="d4">Section XI</data>
      <data key="d5">include all balance sheet assets in their leverage ratio exposure measure, including on-balance sheet derivatives collateral and collateral for SFTs</data>
    </node>
